description: Which side is the axe and which side is the hammer?
name: Golden Hamaxe

description: Normal gloves.
name: Gloves

description: Almost anyone can use this weapon well.
name: Generic Sword

description: It's very easy to carry around, improving your speed!
name: Kitchen Knife

description:
They do a lot of damage if you swing them around hard
enough!
name: Robot Arms

description: :trolley:
name: Small Mallet

description:
It fades from yellow to purple. Sometimes curses the
enemy.
name: Alien Sword

description: Crimson's katana. It's been used a lot.
name: Worn-down Katana

description:
Yes, they attack with stairs.
:csStairBonk:
name: Stairs

description:
Probably not their weapon of choice, but they
use it anyways.
name: Bow

description:
The laptop is very sturdy, so it won't break when you 
smack your enemies with it!
name: Laptop

description: Who uses this? Heck, who even knows where it is?
name: InvisiWeapon

description:
It might sound weaker, but it uses other metals that
are much easier to carry around.
name: Less Golden Hamaxe

description: They have metal plates in them, making them stronger.
name: Strong Gloves

description: Swing it carefully, it hurts when it hits someone.
name: Sharp Sword

description: The gun! It has no bullets...
name: The Gun

description: It zaps whoever it touches for extra damage!
name: Electric Robot Arms

description:
A knife that only heretics can wield. It glows a faint
purple.
name: Heretic Knife

description:
A special weapon for Dirk. Gives the user defense, but
doesn't give much attack.
name: Shield

description:
Sharp blades attached to hands, whether the user has
claws or doesn't in the first place.
name: Sharp Claws

description: A cool blue saber. It glows unrealistically.
name: Blue Saber

description:
Gloves that stick to everything. Lowers your speed 
greatly. Does it have a hidden use...?
name: Sticky Gloves

description:
A stick with a bended blade. Seems inefficient, but I
guess it works.
name: Scythe

description:
Dirk's strongest weapon which he fears using. 
The pattern is outstanding, but it's stained by blood.
name: Dirk

description:
Some might call it salmon color. No one can tell the
difference. Increases your MAG.
name: Pink Saber

description:
Carry this carefully... unless there are a lot of
enemies nearby.
name: Serrated Knife

description: It glows a dark grey. Spooky.
name: Enchanted Scythe

description:
A really big sword. Your speed is lowered because of
how heavy it is.
name: Claymore

description:
The sword is extremely sharp on both sides.
You max HP is decreased greatly.
name: Double Edged Sword

description:
A scythe made to do lots of damage to enemies.
Decreases your MAG stat.
name: Power Scythe

description:
Careful. If you touch it, it'll become normal stairs
again! Somehow, they're stronger than normal ones.
name: Invisible Stairs

description:
It's glowing! I wonder what it's made with... 
Normal attacks sometimes curse the enemy.
name: Glowing Alien Sword

description:
These gloves are made with magical crystals. Wearing
them weakens the user, but strengthens their magic.
name: Crystal Gloves

description:
These gloves have magical runes built into their
fabric, increasing your magic.
name: Spectre Gloves

description:
A band new katana. It doesn't have any chips or
anything.
name: Fresh Katana

description:
In addition to the metal plates, these gloves also have
spikes on the front. Pretty scary.
name: Spiked Gloves

description:
It isn't made with gold anymore. Why did it take us
this long to get here?
name: Not Golden Hamaxe

description: It's extra sharp. It hurts, for sure.
name: Razor Sword

description: It sometimes possesses the enemy when you hit them!
name: Rigged Stairs

description:
...maybe don't use this?
Decreases your hit rate, but increases other stats.
name: Mom's Knife

description:
A sword that only heretics can wield. Similar to the
knife, it glows purple.
name: Heretic Sword

description:
A special weapon. Lowers your SPD and MAG greatly.
However, your basic attack hits 3 times.
name: Disciplinary Hamaxe

description:
A painful knife to hold. Increases your critical
chance by 75%
name: Handleless Knife

description:
It's super bright, and hard to look at. It's somewhat
out of place.
name: Yellow Saber

description:
It's pitch black. Pure darkness. Severely decreases
your magical abilities.
name: Black Saber

description:
A special sword made for knights. Somewhat of a relic,
but it can still be used in battle.
name: Knight's Claymore

description:
Randomly gives out status effects when you attack
the enemy.
name: Mystery Rig Stairs

description:
Increases your attack greatly, and also greatly 
decreases your MP costs as well.
name: Tactical Claws

description:
A special sword made for kings. Unlike similar swords,
it isn't too rare to find.
name: King's Claymore

description:
It's dull, and can barely damage anything. You're
better off just using your fists. Almost always curses.
name: Defective Alien Sword

description:
A corruped sword made of darkness. Only Heretics can
wield it.
name: Heretic Claymore

description:
You must've grinded a lot for this? Was it worth it?
This almost reminds me of something...
name: Very Rare Sword

description:
Your go to choice for scythes when you want more magic.
It grants power as well.
name: Sharpened Scythe

description:
It isn't just electricity anymore. It does damage with
water, fire, air, earth, and other types too!
name: Elemental Robot Arms

description:
It feels like it's about to break in half when you use
it. You must be precise with every swing.
name: Thin Katana

description:
Even though it might not work well for its intended
purpose, it does huge damage when you get hit by it.
name: Old Laptop

description:
You probably shouldn't smack people with it. It looks
fragile.
name: Powerful Laptop

description:
A better version of the normal sticky gloves. It
doesn't have any hidden use this time.
name: Ultra Sticky Gloves

description:
Perfect for artistic defeat of enemies.
Sometimes causes status effects when hitting enemies.
name: Paint Brush

description: The most powerful gloves in existance.
name: Gloves of Calamity

description:
The opposite of the blue one. If you listen closely,
you can hear a heartbeat.
name: Red Saber

description: A sword that only the most evil people can wield.
name: Sword of Darkness

description:
It's probably best to trade this out for a new one.
Provides a little attack.
name: Rusted Scythe

description:
A heavy shield for Dirk. Increases defense stats
greatly, but lowers other stats slightly.
name: Pink Shield

description:
Bright pink gloves. Provides defense, but less attack
compared to other weapons.
name: Pink Gloves

description:
Reeve swapped out your gloves for these. They work
just fine.
name: Challenge Gloves

description:
It's been worn down from use. It's not very strong
anymore.
name: Dull Dirk

description: Reeve's sword. I wonder what it's made out of...?
name: Glowing Sword

description:
A yoyo. Andrew knows how to use it. Increases speed
and max MP greatly.
name: Yoyo

description: A fresh green saber. It increases your magic attack.
name: Green Saber

description:
A sword made for Athens. Seems to be purified in some
way.
name: Purified Sword

description:
A special sword formed using the remains of stars.
Basic attack hits twice.
name: Sunbeam Alien Sword

description:
It's very, very hot... maybe it shouldn't have been
overclocked so much. Burns enemies on hit.
name: Burning Laptop

description:
It's very strong, made with some of the finest 
materials. Brings out your full potential.
name: Legendary Robot Arms
